data.description: Great 3 bedroom home nestled at end of private lane in great location between Burlington & Sedro. Front yard w/ mature landscaping & spacious fully fenced back yard w/ det garage/shop, carport & greenhouse. Large shop has power, heat, piping for woodstove & upgraded ventilation. Recent updates in home include mini-split heat pump/AC, tankless water heater, new lighting/ceiling fans, some flooring & paint. Nice sized bedrooms, kitchen w/plenty of cupboards & garden window. Converted garage creates large bonus room & extra living space. Also has oversized utility area w/ mud entry off side/back yard. Plenty of room to spread out w/ property on both sides of road for extra parking, etc. No HOA! Conveniently located by all amenities & I-5.
